    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When looking at the environmental side of it, how are experts weighing the climate benefits against those equity concerns? Like, is there a general consensus on whether the carbon reduction alone justifies the cost to drivers?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
